## Disclaimer regarding Piracy and Intellectual Property

Lazypub is a tool designed for personal localization, terminology research, and layout management. The developers of Lazypub do not provide EPUB files and are not responsible for the origin of the content you choose to process with this software.

If you are using this tool to translate or modify copyrighted material that you do not own or have a legal right to modify, you do so at your own risk. We do not condone, support, or encourage the unauthorized distribution or piracy of copyrighted works. 

Please support the original authors and publishers by purchasing their books legally. They are the ones who created the content you are currently using AI to avoid reading in its native language. Use this software responsibly and ethically.
